<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Future Life Activation Email</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 768px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: #0070f3; padding: 24px; color: #ffffff;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin: 12px 0; text-align: center;">
                Welcome to Future Life</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 24px;">Hello {{name}}</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Thank you for registering with @FutureLife. To activate your
                account, please go to the following link:</p>
            <h2 style="font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25; margin: 24px; text-align: center;">
                <a href={{verifyUrl}}>{{verifyUrl}}</a>
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Please go to the activation page above within the next 20 minutes.</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">If you did not register for a Future Life account, you can ignore this
                email.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.625; color: rgb(75,85,99);">Need help? Our customer service team is
                here for you 24/7. Visit our <a href='#'
                    style="color:rgb(37,99,235); text-decoration-line: underline;" target="_blank">Help Center</a> or
                contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fl-ecommerce-website-user.vercel.app"
                    style="color:rgb(37,99,235); text-decoration-line: underline'"
                    target="_blank">support@fl-ecommerce-website-user.vercel.app</a>.</p>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>